a.n: The Amazing World of Gumball VI

p.k: The Intelligence / The Potion / The Third / The Debt / The Pressure / The Painting / The Responsible / The Dress / The Laziest Gumball and Darwin argue with the Internet. / The kids find out Dad has been dressing as a woman. / Gumball and Darwin spice up their friendship by introducing a third best friend... / Gumball has to save Mr Robinson’s life during Elmore’s Senior Talent Show! / Gumball tries to save Darwin from being kissed by a girl. / Principal Brown tries to “fix” Gumball’s dysfunctional family. / Gumball and Darwin babysit Anais “responsibly” whilst “irresponsibly” flooding the house. / Gumball goes to school in a dress and becomes the darling of Elmore High. / Gumball and Darwin challenge Dad to a “lazy-off”.
